  <name>SieveEditor</name>
  <summary>ManageSieve script editor for email filtering</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      SieveEditor is a desktop application for creating and managing Sieve email
      filtering scripts on ManageSieve servers. It provides syntax highlighting,
      multi-profile support, and an intuitive interface for editing server-side
      email filters.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Syntax highlighting for Sieve language</li>
      <li>Multi-profile support for multiple email accounts</li>
      <li>ManageSieve protocol support with STARTTLS</li>
      <li>Script validation and activation</li>
      <li>Find and replace with regex support</li>
      <li>HiDPI/4K display support</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
